  <title>WebKit2.WebView::close</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
connect('close', function (webView, ): void);
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Emitted when closing a <link xref="WebKit2.WebView"/> is requested. This occurs when a
call is made from JavaScript's &lt;function&gt;window.close&lt;/function&gt; function.
It is the owner's responsibility to handle this signal to hide or
destroy the <link xref="WebKit2.WebView"/>, if necessary.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>webView</code></title>
<p>instance of <link xref="WebKit2.WebView"/> that is emitting the signal</p>
</item>
